    <item>
      <title>债券市场撤退，作为美国国债，全球范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/treasuries-fire-sale-sends-long-term-yields-soaring-worldwide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自2020年大流行以来，美国国债的回调迅速飙升，随着投资者出售政府债券以筹集现金，这本来可以成为金融动荡和流浪市场的避风港的损失加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/treasuries-fire-sale-sends-long-term-yields-soaring-worldwide</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 05:24:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易战争混乱的股票作为债券幻灯片：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华尔街的另一个混乱的日子看到股票在鞭打，因为投资者试图为唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易战的影响定价，债券的债券滑坡使美国有可能失去避风港地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 22:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
